244
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:25,520
"Something's going on with him.
He's just really jittery."

245
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:27,080
- We need to run.
- Okay.

246
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:28,000
Thanks so much.

247
00:17:28,080 --> 00:17:30,040
Thank you both very much. Good luck.

248
00:17:30,120 --> 00:17:32,800
I took Tom to the side
and just said, "Hey, Tom."

249
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:37,640
