are you hiding something?"

250
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,800
I believe that this person

251
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,680
is not a bad person at all, and just...

252
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:49,200
And our family has felt strongly
for a wh... a while,

253
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:51,520
and there's been a comfort here
for a while

254
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:55,560
that this is just…
somebody who actually likes Elizabeth.

255
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:57,800
We all have issues. If you've...

256
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,560
Anybody who's taken... They...

257
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,680
We've been ripped apart to the core,

258
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:04,120
and we understand
that everybody has issues.

259
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:07,120
This is a wonderful story in a lot of ways

260
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:12,640
because it's about, foremost,
a beautiful little angelic girl.

261
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:15,160
Everybody has issues.

262
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:24,960
Anybody who watches that interview
will think,

263
00:18:25,040 --> 00:18:29,240
"Tom Smart is a crazy son of a bitch,
and maybe he did do it."

264
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:33,080
We came out of that interview,

265
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:36,400
and my wife turned and says,
