276
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:12,000
I mean, I was hearing things.

277
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:15,840
But finding Elizabeth
was the only important thing.

278
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:21,960
I mean, we were never waiting for them
