279
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:24,640
I mean, who gives a shit?
We knew we were cleared.

280
00:19:28,360 --> 00:19:32,560
As a standard in these kinds of cases,
the families get looked at,

281
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,720
and it's really, really tough on them.

282
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:38,480
But their alibis checked out,

283
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:42,480
and with all of the computers we'd seized,
emails that we'd looked at,

284
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:45,680
we did not find anything suspicious.

285
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:49,000
It was dumbfounding

286
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:53,560
as to how long it took the police,
