287
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:59,240
And as the finger was pointed at us,

288
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:03,760
we saw a real drop in people that were…
were coming to help us search.

289
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:08,480
The numbers just took a dive.

290
00:20:09,080 --> 00:20:14,200
I don't think those reporters
realized the impact that they had.

291
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:21,960
But we just keep going,
keep going, keep going.

292
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:26,680
Don't give up.

293
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,120
We got a call.

294
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,720
There were remains found

295
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:38,120
out by the Great Salt Lake
by Interstate 80.

296
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:40,680
It was a female victim.

297
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:47,080
Called Ed and Lois and said,
"Look, we don't know,

298
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:49,600
but potentially, it could be Elizabeth."

299
00:20:54,760 --> 00:20:58,680
The girl's body
