300
00:20:58,760 --> 00:20:59,880
so that there…

301
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:02,880
You know, she could not be recognized.

302
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:15,560
I tried to shield myself
from the raw emotion

303
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:18,040
until it was confirmed.

304
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:26,000
We were able to determine
that it was not Elizabeth.

305
00:21:26,080 --> 00:21:27,760
It was another poor victim.

306
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,880
I felt such a relief,

307
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:40,440
but your mind was just constantly going,
"Where is she? What's happening to her?"

308
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:46,360
I dealt with Ed and Lois every day.
They were strong.

309
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:51,400
In my family, we've experienced
some loss and tragedy,

310
00:21:52,440 --> 00:21:56,280
and I had a basic understanding
of what Ed and Lois were going through.

311
00:21:58,120 --> 00:22:00,200
It hurt to watch them suffer.

312
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:03,480
Elizabeth, if you can hear us,
we love you, Elizabeth.

313
00:22:03,560 --> 00:22:06,040
We haven't forgotten,
and everybody wants you back,

314
00:22:06,120 --> 00:22:07,920
and we won't stop until you're home.

315
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:12,400
The not knowing
is the worst part of anything.

316
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:15,600
What is she going through?
How is she surviving?

317
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:20,040
You know, what could you possibly do
to bring this to a close?

318
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:24,320
<i>The key person in this case
is the nine-year-old sister.</i>

319
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,640
<i>Time is of the essence here.
The clock is ticking.</i>

320
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,200
<i>Right, exactly.</i>

321
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:36,640
The police officers
didn't want me talking to anyone

322
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:39,840
because it would possibly
influence my memory.

323
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:49,600
So I was on my own lonely island,
