368
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:44,600
I didn't have the slightest clue
that Richard was a felon.

369
00:25:45,360 --> 00:25:49,520
He had come recommended
from the church employment center.

370
00:25:49,600 --> 00:25:51,000
So I was shocked.

371
00:25:51,080 --> 00:25:53,280
<i>This 1990 white Jeep Cherokee</i>

372
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:56,440
<i>given to Richard Ricci by Ed Smart
