393
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,920
<i>The man police call a potential suspect…</i>

394
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:30,560
He had done
a lot of work around the house.

395
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:32,480
He had always been very nice.

396
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,600
And, um,

397
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:38,440
I just knew it wasn't Richard Ricci
