410
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:43,520
it seemed, okay,
there's progress being made here.

411
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:48,040
That was blown apart July 24th.

412
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:17,240
Someone tried to break into the home
