00:31:08,800 --> 00:31:12,320
if it's anything
except homicide or kidnapping,

443
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:14,920
we'll offer you immunity from prosecution.

444
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:17,080
Want me to make up some bullshit?

445
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:19,000
No, I don't want you to make up bullshit.

446
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:21,360
Well then, fucking believe me, goddamn it.

447
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:24,040
Well, there's too many things
that don't line up.

448
00:31:24,120 --> 00:31:26,880
F… Find out who the fuck did this shit.

449
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:30,040
So we did the interview
to offer the immunity,

450
00:31:30,120 --> 00:31:32,920
and he and his attorney
were taking that under advisement

451
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,560
when I get a call and they said,

