454
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,440
In Utah, police say the leading suspect

455
00:31:45,520 --> 00:31:48,360
in the disappearance
of 14-year-old Elizabeth Smart has died.

456
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:53,440
<i>Suffering either a stroke
