469
00:32:49,840 --> 00:32:52,000
But honestly, internally…

470
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:56,440
My judgment was that it was very unlikely

471
00:32:56,520 --> 00:32:59,600
we were gonna get
a happy resolution in this case.

472
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:08,640
It seemed like it was a losing battle,

473
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:15,280
but I had this overwhelming feeling
that Elizabeth was still out there.

474
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:22,880
I remember coming home
