475
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:26,360
Lois and I would sit down
and read letters that would come,

476
00:33:27,320 --> 00:33:29,520
and then we fell asleep.

477
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:42,920
I had this dream that Elizabeth
came walking back into our life.

478
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,640
"Oh my God."

479
00:33:52,840 --> 00:33:55,280
"This is… this is… this is over."

480
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:58,880
